---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Learn more about GetLifeSorted.com and our mission to help you make informed financial decisions.">
  <div class="container py-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About GetLifeSorted</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="lead">
          GetLifeSorted.com is dedicated to helping you make informed financial decisions through practical tools and straightforward advice.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          Our mission is to simplify complex financial concepts and provide accessible tools that empower you to take control of your financial future. We believe that everyone deserves access to clear, unbiased information that can help them make better decisions about insurance, savings, investments, and more.
        </p>
        
        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <p>
          GetLifeSorted.com provides two main resources:
        </p>
        
        <h3>Financial Calculators</h3>
        <p>
          Our free calculators help you estimate insurance needs, plan for retirement, calculate savings goals, and more. Each calculator is designed to be easy to use while providing personalized insights based on your specific situation.
        </p>
        
        <h3>Informative Articles</h3>
        <p>
          Our articles cover a wide range of financial topics, from the basics of opening a bank account to more complex subjects like investment strategies. All content is written in plain language with practical advice you can apply to your own financial journey.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Our Approach</h2>
        <p>
          We believe in:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Simplicity</strong> - Financial concepts explained in clear, jargon-free language</li>
          <li><strong>Practicality</strong> - Tools and advice you can actually use in your daily life</li>
          <li><strong>Accessibility</strong> - Free resources available to everyone, regardless of financial knowledge</li>
          <li><strong>Transparency</strong> - Clear information about how our calculators work and where our information comes from</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          While we strive to provide accurate and helpful information, GetLifeSorted.com is not a substitute for professional financial advice. The calculators and articles on this site are for informational purposes only and should not be considered financial or legal advice. Always consult with a qualified professional for specific guidance related to your situation.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          Have questions, suggestions, or feedback? We'd love to hear from you. Please visit our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> to get in touch with our team.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>